{"tid":736521,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大學生緊急呼籲：千祈唔好入浸大！","createTime":"2018-07-10T09:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:36:29.000Z","uid":24160,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ef36491a5540b72415c8503ea4a76dab51693319","tid":736521,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/102226_11cf6b420bd157d9b68181bcd22f7ab1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F102226_11cf6b420bd157d9b68181bcd22f7ab1.jpg&h=e3178e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【良心忠告】臨近Jupas選科最後修改時間，我地一班浸大學生，甘冒天下之大不韙，憑住良心同道德勇氣，同今屆DSE考生講一句忠告:<br />\n「有得揀，千祈唔好入浸大！」<br />\n<br />\n舉四個重大理由畀大家聽，等大家知驚:<br />\n<br />\n一、宇宙最苛刻普通話畢業門檻<br />\n好多人入嚟都唔知，浸大係全港唯一一間有普通話畢業門檻嘅大學。你讀完中小學九年普通話課程，入咗嚟浸大都會逼你讀普通話課程，一個星期讀3個鐘，考拼音對譯、電腦口試，唔合格就唔畀畢業。學生已經通過公投決議取消門檻，但科大、理大相繼改善措施後，只有浸大仍然死攬門檻，繼續殘害學生。如此野蠻，點入得過？<br />\n<br />\n二、大陸學生佔用學位比例最高<br />\n唔好以為大陸學生多唔關你事。BU係全港最高大陸學生比例嘅大學，佔非本地生達94.2%（八大平均為76%）。事實上好多Department都會收多大陸學生，變相收少本地學生，從而推高Jupas分數，所以你睇Jupas分數報名，佢下一年都可以谷高。大陸學生仲專享高額獎學金，每個一年十七萬，就係無本地學生份。<br />\n<br />\n三、中學型家長式 「全人教獄」<br />\n你以為入到大學，課程架構會唔同晒？錯喇，入嚟浸大，你唔係讀緊你想讀個Major，而係讀緊似足中學規格嘅通識課程，要學生讀中文、英文、數學、體育、普通話、宗教、社會科學、理科、商學、歷史、美術、演講（PS）等多不勝數嘅通識課程，質量參差，但全部都計入本科學位嘅Gpa，令你疲於奔命，最後先發覺原來四年光陰心力，都唔係用喺你本來想讀嗰科度；高層口號嘅「全人教育」，淪為學生嘅「全人教獄」。<br />\n<br />\n四、假大空嘅國際化<br />\n有冇聽過浸大要搞國際化，提高海外交流機會？真係信佢一成，雙目失明。校長錢大康話有意「為每名學生提供到大陸或海外地區做交流生、實習或服務學習機會」，但原來「去山區教英文或協助建校」都計算在內。實際浸大海外交流機會實際上遠遠比其他大學都要少。<br />\n<br />\n諸如校園極細、宿位短缺、AR極西、餐廳多蟲等問題太多，罄竹難書。希望DSE同學唔好重蹈覆轍，知道浸大嘅規定同問題，諗真D係咪要揀呢間大學，同樣DSE分數可能仲有好多好選擇。唔好好似我地咁，年年九成九人唔知頭唔知路入嚟中伏！JUPAS開放予同學作「更新課程選擇」時間將於5月23日截止，把握機會，做好決定！大家都快D tag DSE同學，話過佢知啦！"},{"pid":"39ac299fa88cc43bab15ad2b4dd7c18bad906313","tid":736521,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834/1753722628251569/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbumountaingod%2Fphotos%2Fa.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834%2F1753722628251569%2F&d=Tql5HschcrwOX14smS%2Fg%2BsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d665c7ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/photos/a.1569446790012488.1073741828.1569129996710834/1753722628251569/</a>"},{"pid":"26ce272cecffc75c688fdfc136a55be3f7822d9b","tid":736521,"uid":129829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"支持明荃之友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb3a9f47a839600c16d7c0d6ec5c6f5122080c8","tid":736521,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主好有恆心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581c68d755c7c1029b49fc05549f247c28d6dbe6","tid":736521,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"明荃之友入嚟支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff6de5bd60957ccc0d5362b835247883930b3d6","tid":736521,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 咁多女想自己食晒"},{"pid":"4ffb2118fe44d65fb5c00b2903598b1b1997a100","tid":736521,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:24:30.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72e58d4bf8aa925aaef5901fb68215fe4ef257d","tid":736521,"uid":133354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"睇晒成個post都無汪阿姐<br />\n搞錯！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52038415b459f00d6f9e7dea500a707d854069e","tid":736521,"uid":115579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"其實大陸化之後好多間都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,當年走果陣城大已經俾人當係垃圾學店， mainland極多之餘仲要日日j自己國際排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ece1fe94fdb18b77373ca93bff572fd5871c02","tid":736521,"uid":122376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"啱呀咪撚入呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacb2b1effd85e87e364f9e95a3529e1c1f4bf19","tid":736521,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4a45c301cef3aa410774ac8e865f7d3215088a","tid":736521,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"入去食西童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29f431cb02505e3a080ac9d623d5480a597c896","tid":736521,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b4a45c301cef3aa410774ac8e865f7d3215088a","tid":736521,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T09:09:39.00